If you want luxury choose somewhere else but if you just want a reasonable room and are happy with the location, the Sandman Suites are worth considering.	I stayed at the Sandman Suites on Davie for one night and all I can say is that hotel reignited my idea of luxury!	Not a luxury hotel by any means but very practical.	If you can afford it, the Sandman Suites is a good choice.	I would totally recommend this hotel if you are in Vancouver and want to be thrilled with excellent service and friendliness.	If you're planning to walk everywhere, know that the hotel is at the top of a hill that is steep in some directions.